<br>
It depends on the guilds :) I don't know how Triton works, but I know AL and BotS work with a point system where guildmember buy their loot with attendance points. Fair system.<br>
Other guilds work with rolls (yes, it still exists :))<br>
Other guilds have a core of members (be it 15, 20 or 30) that will get important loot and secondary members will get the rest.<br>
Other guilds have the guildleader doing loot and assigning loot as it drops to the members of his guild.<br>
<br>
More or less, in any system, the most important players in a guild get the most interesting pieces of loot first.<br>
